data.description: This charming brick home has been recently updated and offers a spacious layout with two separate living areas, providing plenty of room for relaxation and entertainment. The interior features brand new flooring throughout and boasts an abundance of natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. You'll appreciate the essential upgrades that have been made, including a new water heater and furnace, ensuring comfort and convenience. Additionally, the home is equipped with a modern refrigerated air unit, keeping you cool and comfortable during the warmer months. The expansive .7-acre backyard, offering ample space and an outdoor oasis with endless possibilities for landscaping and creating a wonderful space for family gatherings and fun-filled memories. Make this gem yours today!
